moveMethods.name: level-up
moveMethods.caption: Level up
moveMethods.description: Learned when a Pokémon reaches a certain level.

moveMethods.name: egg
moveMethods.caption: Egg
moveMethods.description: Appears on a newly-hatched Pokémon, if the father had the same move.

moveMethods.name: tutor
moveMethods.caption: Tutor
moveMethods.description: Can be taught at any time by an NPC.

moveMethods.name: machine
moveMethods.caption: Machine
moveMethods.description: Can be taught at any time by using a TM or HM.

moveMethods.name: light-ball-egg
moveMethods.caption: Volt Tackle Pichu
moveMethods.description: Appears on a Pichu whose mother was holding a Light Ball.  The father cannot be Ditto.

moveMethods.name: form-change
moveMethods.caption: Form Change
moveMethods.description: Appears when Rotom or Cosplay Pikachu changes form.  Disappears if the Pokémon becomes another form and this move can only be learned by form change.
